            <div class="column column-5">
                <p>Recognizing that non-profits, foundations and companies have a need to demonstrate  their work’s vital role in the community, One Story Productions launched in 2007. 
For each client we create a unique brand development plan. First we sit down together. We document goals and expectations based on an understanding of what’s important and how a brand film can best fit within larger marketing / brand strategy. </p>
                <p>Through collaboration, we create visual voices that tell real stories. 
